lead_paragraph: A.J. Griffin got the victory in his first major league appearance in more than two seasons and Rougned Odor homered, leading the Texas Rangers over the Los Angeles Angels 7-3 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Rangers Beat Angels 7-3 in Griffin's 1st Start Since 2013
